  "original_title": "\u0dc0\u0dd3 \u0db8\u0dd9\u0da7\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0dd2\u0d9a\u0dca\u0da7\u0ddc\u0db1\u0dca \u0dbd\u0d9a\u0dca\u0dc2\u0dba\u0d9a\u0dca \u0d9c\u0db1\u0dca\u0db1 \u0db8\u0dab\u0dca\u0da9\u0dbd\u0dba \u0dad\u0dd3\u0dbb\u0dab\u0dba \u0d9a\u0dbb\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The board decides to take 100,000 metric tons of V",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Ministry of Agriculture says that the Paddy Marketing Board has planned to buy 100,000 metric tons of the paddy harvest of the Yala season.",
        "The ministry says that it is proposed to spend an amount of 10,500 million rupees for this purpose and arrangements have been made to get approval from the cabinet next week.",
        "In determining the price for one kilogram of paddy, the Minister of Agriculture instructed the Commissioner General of Agricultural Services to find out how much it costs the farmers to cultivate paddy per hectare and submit a report, and to consider that cost and decide the price of one kilogram.",
        "The Ministry says that the Minister has taken steps to appoint a committee to determine the price of paddy and the Secretary of the Ministry of Agriculture has been nominated as the chairman of that committee.",
        "On the recommendation of the said committee, the price per kilogram of paddy is decided and it is proposed to announce the said price as per the approval of the Council of Ministers. The paddy marketing board will announce the price of a kilogram of paddy purchased next week"
      ],
